a year. This is an optional extra and it’s completely up to you whether you renew. If you don't wish to continue using your domain proxy package, you can simply delete it via your control panel with a single click.</p></div></li></ul></div></section><div class="container padding-md"><div class="col-12"><p class="lead txt-center padding-bottom-sm"><strong>Register domain names</strong> now, or if you have any questions, don’t hesitate to contact us.</p></div><div class="col-8 push-2"><div class="domain-search-wrapper channel-ds"><div class="form-wrapper"><form action="/search/domain" class="domain-search-form auto-complete" id="domain-names-DS-newcust" method="post" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded"><ul><li class=" required-element  text-element" id="keyword_2-field"><input data-auto-complete="true" data-default-suffix=".com" data-backend="streaming" type="text" name="keyword" id="keyword_2" class="keyword" maxlength="100" required="required" placeholder="Search for your perfect domain..." aria-label="enter domain name..."/><span class="domain-ghost"></span></li><li class=" optional-element  button-element" id="submit_btn_2-field"><button  name="submit_btn" id="submit_btn_2" class="btn" type="submit" value="Search"></button> </li></ul><input  type="hidden" name="group" id="group_2" class="group"/> <input  type="hidden" name="suffix" id="suffix_2" class="group suffix"/> </form></div></div></div></div><div class="disclaimer bg-light"><div class="container"><div class="col-12 txt-center padding-md"><p>* The following suffixes are on offer for &pound;0.00&nbsp; when registered for 1 year using the embedded voucher code - .CO.UK. &amp; .UK &amp; .ORG.UK. This offer applies to new purchases only. The following suffix is on offer for &pound;1.99&nbsp; when registered for 1 year using the embedded voucher code - .COM. The offer applies to new purchases only. These offers limit you to one &pound;0.00&nbsp; .CO.UK domain, one &pound;0.00&nbsp; .UK domain, one &pound;